hyper-personalized environments through the inte-grated control of
lighting, fragrance, and sound. Based on the user's registered devices,
preferences, and contextual data, the system automatically recommends or
adjusts the optimal ``mood scene.'' Users can also manually modify each
element through intuitive interfaces within the application.

1)Mood Recommendation and Scene Generation

a)Context-Aware Analysis

